### Get contact submissions (admin - requires token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/contact
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Mark a contact as read (admin - requires token)
# Replace {{contactId}} with an actual id from the Get response
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/contact/{{contactId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
